# ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡¿ CzechFabric SDK

The official Python SDK for accessing the **Czech Intelligence Fabric (MCP)** - a unified API for Czech public services including transport, geolocation, and contextual AI tooling.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Plan public transport trips using OpenTripPlanner
- ğŸš Real-time departures from stop names or coordinates
- ğŸ—ºï¸ Geocode / Reverse-geocode locations
- ğŸ“ Find nearby stops
- ğŸ“¦ Fetch stop metadata and zone info
- ğŸ§  List available tools and generate LLM-friendly summaries
- ğŸ” Built-in retry, caching, and error handling

---

## ğŸ“¦ Installation

```bash
pip install czechfabric-sdk
````

